     * Padding is added to account for lack of signature on transaction
     * 1 byte for RLP V prefix
     * 1 byte for V
     * 1 byte for RLP R prefix
     * 32 bytes for R
     * 1 byte for RLP S prefix
     * 32 bytes for S
